e exclusion of any other remedy", "confidence_score": 0.9}, {"summary": "by Lessee and Lessee''s Insurance Lessee shall be responsible for and shall relieve, indemnify and save Lessor harmless from and against (a) all liabil...", "risk_flag": "medium", "clause_type": "insurance", "original_text": "Indemnification by Lessee and Lessee''s Insurance\nLessee shall be responsible for and shall relieve, indemnify and save Lessor harmless from\nand against (a) all liability for loss of life, personal injury and/or damage to property occurring in\nor around the Premises including, but not limited to any claims made by Lessee''s agents, vendors,\nservice providers, guests, invitees, clients, customers, investors or patrons and (b) any loss or\ndamage from Lessee''s failure to perform its obligations under this Lease", "confidence_score": 0.8}, {"summary": "Lease supersedes and cancels any and all previous negotiations, arrangements, brochures, agreements and understandings, if any, between the parties he...", "risk_flag": "low", "clause_type": "use_restrictions", "original_text": "This Lease supersedes and cancels any\nand all previous negotiations, arrangements, brochures, agreements and understandings, if any,\nbetween the parties hereto or displayed by Lessor to Lessee with respect to the subject thereof, and\nnone thereof shall be used to interpret or construe this Lease", "confidence_score": 0.8}, {"summary": "of Lease If any clause or provision of this Lease is legally invalid, the remaining clauses and provisions of this Lease shall remain in full force an...", "risk_flag": "low", "clause_type": "use_restrictions", "original_text": "Validity of Lease\nIf any clause or provision of this Lease is legally invalid, the remaining clauses and\nprovisions of this Lease shall remain in full force and effect", "confidence_score": 0.8}], "cam_charges": "Tenant responsible for common area maintenance charges", "summary_text": "Subleasing requires written consent from the landlord. The landlord has discretionary approval rights.", "restrictions_summary": "Premises may only be used for any claims made by lessee''s agents. Subleasing and assignment require written landlord consent. Lease may be terminated for tenant defaults as specified.", "permissibility_status": "requires_permission", "responsibilities_summary": "Tenant responsible for maintaining fencing, interior fixtures, equipment, premises repairs. Tenant responsible for insurance requirements as specified. Tenant must indemnify and hold landlord harmless from specified liabilities. Tenant must remove signage and repair related damage upon lease termination."}', '2025-08-22 15:47:09.762152+00', '2025-08-22 15:47:09.762152+00', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Tenant responsible for common area maintenance charges', NULL, NULL);
